raw_text = "~ start
## 6pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Mabel: Finally freeee 😮‍💨
Player: Finished classes? So late!
Mabel: It was an extended optional class for anyone who thinks they need it 🥹
Mabel: It wouldn't hurt to be extra prepared right??
Mabel: So glad it's finally done though
Mabel: Heading home now, I just wanna collapse and sleep forever!
- Make sure you rest up
	Player: Make sure you rest up!
	Mabel: Thanks babe
- Wish you could collapse with me
	Player: Wish you could collapse with me
	Mabel: Omg 🥰
	Mabel: Someone is extra sweet today 😚
	Mabel: I'd love that so much hehe
do Story.set_location(\"college_square_gardens\")
Player: Long week huh
Mabel: The LONGEST 😩
Mabel: The sun's totally gone again 😱😭
do heart(1)
Mabel: I guess winter is coming around huh 😣
Mabel: My legs are so stiff
- It'll go easy like last time!
	Player: It'll go easy like last time!
	Mabel: Thought: I'm a little worried it might go like last time
	Mabel: You're probably right 😊
- I'll be here every step of the way!
	Player: I'll be here every step of the way!
	Mabel: Awwh, come here and hold my hand 🥰
	Mabel: I won't be scared if you're here hehe
	Mabel: My hero 🩷
Mabel: Okay I'll take the shortcut through town again
Mabel: Thought: Ugh, walking in the dark is the worst 😣
Mabel: Thought: Maybe if I close my eyes and pretend...
Mabel: sfx: highmoan3: Eep!!
do heart(2)
Mabel: sfx: none: Oh! S-sorry
Mabel: Thought: Auuugh not this again
Mabel: sfx: none: H-hi... again
Mabel: Thought: Oh gosh, that guy again. We keep bumping into each other huh..
do echo_set([\"210\"])
Mabel: sfx: none: I'm on my way home again
Mabel: Thought: Okay just be polite and keep walking, don't make it weird
Mabel: One sec babe! 😋
Player: Everything okay?
Mabel: Totally fine!!
Mabel: sfx: none: Walk me home?
Mabel: Thought: Say no Mabel. You can do it! Be brave!!
Mabel: sfx: none: Oh no no
Mabel: sfx: none: I'm okay on my own really!
Mabel: sfx: none: Haha you really don't have to, it's not even far!
Mabel: Thought: Please just take the hint and gooo
Mabel: Thought: Or maybe don't... I don't wanna walk alone
Mabel: sfx: none: I-I insist, it's totally fine!
Mabel: Thought: But it's SO dark out
Mabel: Thought: And there's literally not a single other person around
Mabel: Thought: Honestly some company wouldn't be the worst thing...
Mabel: Thought: The walk goes faster like this I guess
Mabel: PinkThought: and he is kind of big...
Mabel: Thought: I HATE that I'm even thinking about this
Mabel: sfx: none: Okay, I guess
Mabel: sfx: none: If you really insist
Mabel: Thought: What do you even say to someone who triple insists...
do Story.set_location(\"main_street\")
Mabel: Making good time 😅
Player: Glad to hear!
Mabel: Thought: Save me babe
Mabel: What are you doing right now?
- Making sure you get home safe!
	Player: Making sure you get home safe!
	Mabel: Awwh you're SO sweet
	Mabel: Thought: I don't care that this guy is walking with me, babe is with me in spirit hehe
- Multi-tasking
	Player: Multi-tasking
	Mabel: Thanks for caring about me when you're so busy 🥺
	Mabel: Thought: I wish I wasn't such a burden on babe...
	Mabel: PinkThought: Does this guy think I'm a burden too?
Mabel: sfx: none: Oh.. just my uhm... my friend...
Mabel: Thought: Sorry, babe!!
Mabel: sfx: none: She..? Oh haha, yeah it's uhm... a girl.
Mabel: Thought: Double sorry!!
Mabel: sfx: none: Cute when I'm nervous..? Uh thanks
do echo_clear()
Mabel: sfx: highmoan1: Eep!
do Story.mabel_groped(\"RawDawg\")
Mabel: sfx: none: U-um...
do echo_set([\"211\"])
Mabel: sfx: highmoan2: Nghh!
do heart(3)
Mabel: Thought: His arm, it's wrapped around my waist
Mabel: PinkThought: Our bodies are super close
Mabel: Thought: and why are we walking super slow all of a sudden
Mabel: sfx: highmoan4: Hngh!
Mabel: PinkThought: My legs are... shaking a bit less I think
Mabel: PinkThought: He's holding me so.. tightly...
Mabel: Thought: But if I tell him no... would I have to walk home alone?
Mabel: Thought: Take advantage of him Mabel. It's a free walk home after all
Mabel: sfx: none: H-haha, it-... it's just up here, almost there
Mabel: Baeb, u still ther?
Player: Yeah? Something wrong?
Mabel: Jjust wanted to say I missed you
Player: Missed you too!
Mabel: Thought: What did that even accomplish, it's not like babe is here
Mabel: Thought: Babe would totally tell this guy off! Yeah.. meanie!
Mabel: Thought: Make up your mind Mabel!! Is he a friend or bad guy??
Mabel: Thought: Phew, we made it though
do echo_clear()
do heart(1)
Mabel: sfx: none: A reward? For walking me you mean?
Mabel: sfx: none: S-sure... Anything I can do, I g-guess..
Mabel: Thought: I guess I owe him something
Mabel: sfx: none: My number?
Mabel: Thought: I shouldn't. I really shouldn't do that!
Mabel: sfx: none: Is there something else... heh
Mabel: sfx: none: A K-Kiss!?
Mabel: sfx: none: Okay he-here's my number haha, I guess
Mabel: Thought: Th-there's no way I'd ever kiss another b-boy, just take my number and shoo!
Mabel: Thought: He has my Socials anyway, what more could this do
Mabel: sfx: none: O-okay um.. here, it's.. this
Mabel: Thought: ...I just gave a total stranger my number...
do advance_time(0, 5)
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do heart(1)
Mabel: I'm home safe and sound, finally
Player: See? You always make it 😌
- Keep doing what you're doing!
	Player: Keep doing what you're doing!
	Mabel: Y-yeah haha
	Mabel: Thought: Oh babe, if only you knew
- Soon you'll be able to do it all on your own!
	Player: Soon you'll be able to do it all on your own!
	Mabel: Y-yeah haha
	Mabel: Thought: I hope so, I don't wanna keep relying on him..
Mabel: Thought: He has my number now
Mabel: Thought: Why did I do that?
Mabel: Thought: Oh right! Because a kiss is definitely out of the question!!
Mabel: Okay I am beyond done today, gonna pass out 😴
Mabel: Night babe, talk tomorrow
Player: Night Mabes
Mabel: Love u 🩷
do heart(0)
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
